verbose_text: Without odor exposure, TMEM16F expressing axons did not degenerate with age : although they were much dimmer than controls in 3-day-old flies (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY and XREF_FIG), the signals increased rapidly in 5-day-old flies (XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG) and further increased in 25-day-old flies (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY, and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
